'''Anton''' is a smith who runs the [[Warrior Guild Armoury]] where he sells various types of [[armour]]. He is located on the {{FloorNumber|uk=1}} of the [[Warriors' Guild]], located in [[Burthorpe]].

Anton talks to himself as he makes the rounds of his shop, extolling the virtues of his wares, but also stating "Ow, my toe! That armour is heavy." for a bit of armoury humour.

